        "description": "<p>This plugin allows you to shorten or hide the description under each widget on the the widgets admin page.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>trim-widget-descriptions</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Go to /wp-admin/widgets.php to change the description length.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>0.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated ellipsis function.</li>\n<li>Works in WP 4.2.0. </li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor code clean up and verify compatibility with WordPress 3.8.1.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added deactivation hook.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial build of plugin. Nothing fancy.</li>\n</ul>\n"
